data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home nestled in the heart of Newburgh. Boasting a finished walk-out basement, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers ample space for comfortable living. The main level features a cozy living room, a spacious eat-in kitchen perfect for gatherings, and a convenient deck just outside for outdoor dining and relaxation. Downstairs, a huge family room awaits, providing additional space for entertainment or relaxation. With its desirable layout and convenient location, this home is a must-see for those seeking both comfort and functionality.
